<plot>A documentary about the codependent relationship between Batman and his rogues' gallery of villains, exploring the layered psychology behind the characters and the natures of heroism and villainy. DC Comics writers and editors provide a historical perspective to the discussion as it relates to the new animated feature _Batman: Gotham Knight (2008) (V)_ (qv).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?013338</url></doc>
